style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> <a href="https://t.co/j2ASuXmLxW">pic.twitter.com/j2ASuXmLxW</a></p><p> — 蕾妮<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1fab7.png" alt="🪷" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> （@PettyLupone） <a href="https://twitter.com/PettyLupone/status/1852802862616867056?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 11 月 2 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p> “卡马拉·哈里斯将保护你在政策或想法上不同意她的权利，”他补充道。 “然后，就像我们几个世纪以来所做的那样，我们将辩论它们，我们将共同努力解决它们，然后我们将继续前进。</p><p>他在结束这段视频时总结道：“另一个人，他要求毫无疑问的忠诚，说他想要复仇。我是哈里森·福特。我和其他人一样只有一票，我将用它来前进。我将投票给卡马拉·哈里斯。”</p><p>他加入了越来越多的娱乐界人物的行列，支持哈里斯，哈里斯得到了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/beyonce">碧昂斯、</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charli-xcx-john-legend-and-more-endorse-kamala-harris-for-us-president-3776745">查理·XCX</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/joni-mitchell-shares-her-thoughts-on-the-us-elections-fuck-donald-trump-3804542">乔尼·米切尔</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chappell-roan">查普尔·罗恩</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/megan-thee-stallion-slams-those-avoiding-presidential-election-what-the-fuck-are-you-talking-about-3790934">梅根·泰·斯塔林</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/cher-endorses-kamala-harris-im-so-grateful-to-be-able-to-make-my-voice-count-this-year-3804267">雪儿</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lizzo-speaks-at-kamala-harris-rally-hits-out-at-donald-trumps-comments-about-detroit-3804404">利佐</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/obama-raps-lose-yourself-verse-at-kamala-harris-rally-after-being-introduced-by-eminem-3805325">阿姆</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/usher-joins-kamala-harris-at-atlanta-rally-everything-we-do-in-the-next-17-days-will-affect-our-children-and-grandchildren-3804493">亚瑟小子</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-pnk-perform-what-about-us-with-daughter-to-close-democratic-national-convention-3786178">P!nk</a> 、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/leonardo-dicaprio">莱昂纳多·迪卡普里奥</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/leonardo-dicaprio-and-bad-bunny-have-endorsed-kamala-harris-3806836">坏兔子的</a>支持， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-bon-iver-perform-at-kamala-harris-rally-in-wisconsin-3781912">Bon Iver</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/quavo-backs-kamala-harris-for-tackling-gun-violence-at-atlanta-rally-3779672">Quavo</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billie-eilish">Billie Eilish</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/olivia-rodrigo">Olivia Rodrigo</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-mumford-sons-push-for-voting-plan-as-they-perform-at-kamala-harris-rally-3808418">Mumford &amp; Sons</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/evanescence">Evanence</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Finneas">Finneas 的 Amy Lee。</a></p><p>前总统特朗普的支持者包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kid-rock-shares-his-thoughts-on-taylor-swift-and-eminem-endorsing-kamala-harris-3807296">Kid Rock</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/kelsey-grammer-banned-from-talking-about-trump-support-in-interviews-reporter-claims-3553743">Kelsey Grammer</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-makes-a-brief-appearance-at-donald-trump-supporters-rally-in-beverly-hills-3784869">Kanye West</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/hulk-hogan-asks-crowd-if-they-want-him-to-body-slam-kamala-harris-3786054">Hulk Hogan</a> 。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/harrison-ford-endorses-kamala-harris-and-tim-walz-these-are-people-i-can-get-behind-3809065">哈里森·福特支持卡玛拉·哈里斯和蒂姆·沃尔兹的帖子：“这些是我可以支持的人”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
